FBIS4-60961 "drsov084_m_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-084 Daily Report 29 Apr 1994 Tajikistan State of Emergency Extended in Khatlon Oblast State of Emergency Extended in Khatlon Oblast LD2904161594 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1100 GMT 29 Apr 94 LD2904161594 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] In order to stabilize the situation, enforce the law, and protect citizens, the Presidium of Tajikistan's National Assebmly has extended by three months, until 30 July, the emergency situation in Khatlon Oblast.
